{
  "stem": "268.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We're talking mid-30s, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he was in the business and so he-- he-- I remember, he bought a big console, which three bands, three or four bands.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I would listen to-- I would listen to music from Germany, from Czechoslovakia, in different languages.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Especially on short wave I would catch it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Sometimes BBC from England.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I didn't understand a word what they were saying, but I would listen to the music.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I remember my first introduction to the upbeat music.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I remember Benny Goodman.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had no idea who they were, but the music was almost like a signature, and i could tell, this has-- it's got to be Benny Goodman or Glenn Miller, you know?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Later on, the names became more-- more familiar, but until I heard-- I heard the music, it was really strange because I was used to listening to either Polish stations or German stations, with the marches, you know, and Wagnerian music.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- and this all of a sudden I could tap my foot to.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, I felt, you know, [? very ?] happy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that was my favorite part of the-- of the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Worked the dial, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I used to imitate different stations and different announcers, where he had different languages.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Didn't know what they were saying, but the sound, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remember listening to the Czech stations, and I will announce what now we would call station break.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They would say, radio--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SPEAKING POLISH] I used to imitate it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I thought it sounded funny.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But those are fond memories of childhood and what you could do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you asked me about favorite room, this was it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Soccer games were not broadcast very often, unless they were international games.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
